## make network object
RA_N <- set_agd_arm(reshaped_RA_data,study=Study,trt=Treatment,r=ACR20_k,n=ACR20_N,trt_ref = "Placebo")

RA_N

## plot
plot(RA_N,weight_edges = TRUE, weight_nodes = TRUE, nudge = 0.075) + 
  ## Nudge the legend over
  ggplot2::theme(legend.box.spacing = ggplot2::unit(0.75, "in"),
                 plot.margin = ggplot2::margin(0.1, 0, 0.1, 0.75, "in"))

## run NMA
RA_NMA  <- nma(RA_N,
               seed = 123456,
               trt_effects = "random", ## fixing a random effects model here
               prior_intercept = normal(scale = 100),
               prior_trt = normal(scale = 100),
               prior_het = half_normal(scale = 2.5),
               adapt_delta = 0.98)
